Zero once again took the lazers blasts into his wings before firing 
back at Barrymore with a blast of matrix energy before he sped 
towards her and tried to slash her with his energy sabre. However 
before he reached her his optics began to glow a right green as he 
looked to the sky and saw the massive form of Gemini Dragon and also 
another... familiar form... Rather then continue his attack on 
Barrymore he sped past her in the direction of Trainwreck and Methos.
